reviewText: The case pictured is a soft violet color, but the case cover I received was a dark purple. While I'm sure the quality of the product is fine, the color is very different.

The case is super cute, durable, and a conversation starter. The delivery was before the estimated date, and the case it's self is well made.Since it's 2 separate pieces, it isn't perfectly snug, so i slip a little piece of paper on my phone before I put on the dripping part. reviewText: I had to super glue the two parts together because it would come apart and my phone would slide out of the case and fall. Also the color is much more bland than in the picture

I ordered this as a birthday present for my sister. It arrived quickly, but I was very disappointed. As excited as I was to purchase this item, the day that it arrived had me on cloud 9. No more worrying about potentially dropping my phone and breaking it. However sadly this case was not worth the money invested. The top piece did not fit with the bottom piece so one sad day at Disneyland,upon retrieving my phone, the top piece slid right off, remaining in my hands while my iPhone hit the asphalt, cracking right down the middle. Clearly purchasing this case was a HUGE mistake.

reviewText: I was expecting a cute case that fit my Verizon iPhone 4S well. I got it in the mail and I was so excited to try it on my phone. It barely fits. The button holes don't fit the buttons. (Too high up) Another thing is the melt thingies near the fromt canera and stuff kept peeling my screen protector off whenever i tried to put it on. i fell head over heels with this case and I'm so upset it doesn't fit right.. If you have the Verizon iPhone 4S, sadly, beware..

reviewText: Although I received this case very quickly, mine seems to be a dud. The top and bottom parts slide together, but do not lock in place.
